name: Candy Apple Red 1988 - 1989 Fender Stratocaster
description:
One of the most popular musical instruments in history, the Fender Stratocaster is certainly one of the most imitated electric guitars ever. Fender's Comfort Contour Body, 3 single-coil pickups and bright, clean, "twangy" sound are standard for the Strat, designed byFender back in 1954. From Buddy Holly and Hendrix to Stevie Ray Vaughan and beyond, the Strat continues to be one of modern music's Holy Grails.

Corona Plant (Fender), USA
in the Year(s): 1988 - 1989

name: Gibson Les Paul Custom Electric Guitar ( Ebony Finish )
description:
Features
One-piece mahogany neck
Carved maple top
Warm-toned mahogany body
24-3/4" scale
Richlite fingerboard
22 frets
Figured acrylic block inlays
Gold hardware
490R neck humbucker with Alnico II magnets
498T bridge humbucker with Alnico V magnets
Nashville Tune-O-Matic bridge with stopbar tailpiece
Tulip tuners
Body, neck, and headstock binding
1-11/16" nut width


Nashville Plant, TN, USA
March 4th, 1991
Production Number: 75

name: Metal Mafia Worldwide Social Club ( one year band membership )
description:
Metal Mafia Worldwide's is a social club . Our goal is simple . Keep the hard rock and heavy metal scene alive all over the world . 
By organizing and hosting regular shows & charity events featuring unsigned and indie signed bands from all over .

Dues 
Yearly dues are $ 25.00

As a member you get : 
1. You get your patch ( that shows you are an active member of the M.M.W ) 
2. You get a 50 % discount on all regular Metal Mafia Worldwide sponsored shows ( this does not apply to charity events ) 
3. Plus you get a 50 % discount on any future M.M.W merchandise
* Bands must be members in order to be considered for shows .
